```plantuml
@startuml

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

interface Invoker <<(I,#7B68EE)>> {
}

interface Command <<(I,#7B68EE)>> {
    execute()
    undo()
}

interface Client <<(I,#7B68EE)>> {
}

class ConcreteCommand <<(C,#90EE90)>> {
    execute()
    undo()
}

interface Receiver <<(I,#7B68EE)>> {
    action()
}

Invoker --> Command
ConcreteCommand ..|> Command
Client --> ConcreteCommand
Client --> Receiver
ConcreteCommand --> Receiver

note top of Invoker : 调用者持有命令对象，\n并在某刻调用execute()

note top of Command : 调用命令对象的execute()\n就可以让接收者进行动作

note right of Client : 这个客户负责创建一个\nConcreteCommand，并\n设置其接受者

note left of ConcreteCommand : 定义了动作和接收者之间\n的绑定关系，调用者只需\n要调用execute()就可以\n发出请求

note bottom of Receiver : 接收者知道如何实现这个请求

@enduml
```